# denlockhart.com

Static site hosting Dennis Lockhart's side projects. Not a single-app repo.

## Structure

- **Site shell:** `index.html`, `site.css` at repo root
- **Projects:** `projects/<slug>/` — each app is self-contained
- **Hosting:** `netlify.toml` — rewrites short URLs (e.g. `/army-builder/`) to project folders

## Current projects

| Slug | Folder | URL |
|------|--------|-----|
| army-builder | `projects/army-builder/` | `/army-builder/` |

## Defaults for agents

- Scope changes to the relevant project folder unless editing the home page or Netlify config
- User-specific saved data goes in browser localStorage, not the repo
- See `AGENTS.md` for full instructions; see `projects/<slug>/README.md` for project details
- Create commits when completing work; push only when asked

